1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:06,400
This goo is liquid and solid at the same time — and you can punch it!

2
00:00:06,400 --> 00:00:10,800
Meet oobleck, a non-Newtonian fluid made of just cornstarch and water.

3
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:13,600
When poured, it flows like a liquid...

4
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:16,800
but strike it hard, and it becomes solid!

5
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:20,400
This shear thickening effect makes oobleck fascinating and fun!

6
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:24,800
Check this out: the harder you hit, the firmer it gets!

7
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:26,800
Perfect for some science comedy.

8
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:28,800
Ready to try oobleck yourself?

9
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:31,600
Hit that follow for more wild science!
